{{DISPLAYTITLE:LIBXC2_Pn}}
{{TAGDEF|LIBXC2_Pn|[real]}}

Description: {{TAG|LIBXC2_Pn}}, where <math>n=1, 2, \ldots</math> allows to specify the values of the parameters of the functional implemented in Libxc that is called with {{TAG|LIBXC2}}.
----

A detailed explanation on how to use {{TAG|LIBXC1_Pn}} and {{TAG|LIBXC2_Pn}} and an example can be found at the {{TAG|LIBXC1_Pn}} page.

